edu.stanford.nlp.neural

Class SimpleTensor

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.neural.SimpleTensor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class SimpleTensor
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class defines a block tensor, somewhat like a three dimensional matrix. This can be created in various ways, such as by providing an array of SimpleMatrix slices, by providing the initial size to create a 0-initialized tensor, or by creating a random matrix.
    Author:
    John Bauer, Richard Socher
    See Also:
